Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:23.02,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,I need to attain the Legendary Pokémon’s power \N and send it to that weapon once again!{densetsu no pokemon no power o te ni ire, futatabi ano heiki e okurikomanakyanaranai no da!}{EN game: I need to reclaim the Legendary Pokémon's power and send it to that weapon once again.}{JP game: 伝説ポケモンが 取り戻した　能力を 再び　最終兵器に 送りこまねば　ならない=I need to send the power that the Legendary Pokemon has regained into the Ultimate Weapon once more.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.70,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,Damn it all!{kusoyarou!}{EN game: Whaugh!}{JP game:ウオォッ！！=Ahhh!!}{Normally, I'd want to replace the "damn", but I can't really think of anything better, and I think it's probably fine what with these shorts being more "edgy". - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.84,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,Everything beautiful...{utsukushii mono wa subete,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.70,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,...should stay that way...{sono mama de aru beki da.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.08,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,...forever.{eien ni.}{EN game: Everything beautiful should stay that way forever.}{JP game: いつまでも　美しく　ある=To be eternally beautiful, [isn't that your duty as an actress?]}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:44.97,Main,Carnet,0,0,150,,You can’t equate youth with beauty. \N It’s inevitable that everything changes.{wakasa equal utsukushisa to wa kagiranaishi. monogoto wa nandemo, kawaru no yo.}{EN game: Youth may be beautiful, but it’s not all there is to life. Everything changes.}{JP game: 若さ　イコール　美しさ　とは 限らないし　なんでも　変わるのよ=You can't equate youth with beauty. Everything changes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:49.52,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,150,,But I would make a world where \N everything beautiful lasts forever.{watashinara utsukushii mono subete ga eien ni kawaranai sekai o tsukurimasu.}{EN game: I would make this world unchanging and eternal so all beauty will last forever.}{JP game: わたしなら　世界を 永遠の　ものとして すべての　美しさを いつまでも　保つかもしれない=If it were me, I might make the world eternal, and preserve everything beautiful forever.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.44,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,150,,This world will eventually reach \N a point of no return...{kono yo wa yagate hikikaesanai tokoro made iku deshou.}{EN game: This world will eventually reach the point of no return...}{JP game:世界は　やがて　行き詰る……=The world will someday reach an impasse...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.49,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,150,,I will put an end to Pokémon.{Pokemon ni wa kietemoraimasu.}{EN game: Pokémon... Shall no longer exist.}{JP game: ポケモンには 消えてもらう=I will have Pokémon begone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:59.38,Main,Platane,0,0,150,,Even if that may be the case, \N that doesn’t mean you’re right!{sono kanousei wa aru kamoshirenai ga, sore ga tadashii to wa kagiranai!}{EN game: That being said, what Lysandre says is only one way of looking at things... It’s not necessarily the truth.}{JP game: とはいえ　フラダリさんの　いうことは あくまでも　一つの　考え…… 正しいとは　限らないからね=That being said, what Mr. Fleur-de-Lis says is only one way of thinking... It's not necessarily correct.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.89,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,150,,Kalos is beautiful.{kalos-chihou wa utsukushii}{EN game: Kalos is beautiful!}{JP game: カロスは　美しい！=Kalos is beautiful!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:05.19,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,150,,I can’t stand the thought \N of the world becoming uglier.{sekai ga minikuku kawatteiku no wa taeraren!}{EN game: I can’t stand the thought of the world becoming uglier.}{JP game: 世界が　醜く 変わっていくのは　堪えられません=I can't bear the world becoming uglier.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:23.43,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,I don’t expect that you will understand \N how I think and feel.{watashi no kangae ya kanjiteiru koto o rikaishitemoraou to wa omowanai.}{EN game: I don’t expect that I will ever make you understand how I think and feel...}{JP game: わたしの　想い…… わかってもらおうとは　思わない=My thoughts... I don't think I can have you understand them.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:34.98,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,The original purpose of this device \N was to give life, not take it!{kono souchi no honrai no mokuteki wa, inochi o ataeru koto de atte, ubau tame de wa nai!}{EN game: The original purpose of this device was to bring a Pokémon back to life.}{JP game: 元は　死んだ　ポケモンを 生き返らせるための　装置=This was originally a device to bring dead Pokemon back to life.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:39.57,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,There’s not much power left... \N But there is enough to use it once.{amari power wa nokottenai ga, ikkai dake nara juubun darou.}{EN game:There's not much power left... But there IS enough to use it once...}{JP game:出力を　抑えれば 望む　結果は　得られるか……=If I limit the output, I can get the result I desire, hmm...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.64,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,I shall grant you eternal life.{eien no inochi o sazuketeyarou.}{EN game: I shall grant you eternal life!}{JP game:枯れない　命だ！=Lives without death!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:55.05,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,I’ll give you the pain of endlessly waiting \N for a beautiful world to finally be built!{utsukushii sekai ga jitsugen suru sono toki made machitsudzukeru kurushimi o ajiwae!}{EN game: I'll give you the pain of endlessly waiting for a beautiful world to finally be built!}{JP game: 美しい　世界を　つくるまで 死ねない　苦しみを　くれてやる！！=I'll grant you the pain of never dying, until a beautiful world is built!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.48,Main,Team Flare,0,0,0,,The device was activated!{Souchi ga hatsudou shita!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.24,Main,Bald Flair Man,0,0,0,,Quick!{Hayaku shiro!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.40,Main,Bald Flair Man,0,0,0,,The exit’s that way!{Deguchi wa atchi da!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:13.90,Main,Bald Flair Man,0,0,0,,Hurry!{Isoge!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.65,Main,Team Flare,0,0,0,,Right!{Hai!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.59,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,Let us live forever!{Eien ni ikiyou de wa nai ka!!!!!}{EN game: Let us live forever...}{JP game: わたしと　永遠に　生きよう……=Live forever, with me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:23.93,Main,Pachira,0,0,0,,Revelations from recent events \N have left the people of Kalos in great shock.{Konkai no ken de, shinjitsu o shitta Kalos-chihou no hitobito wa, ooki na shock o uketeimasu.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:29.35,Main,Pachira,0,0,0,,Today, let us reflect on this message \N that Mr. Fleur-de-Lis once recorded.{So I’d like you to see this recording \N Mr. Fleur-de-Lis once made.}{De wa, izen satsuei sareta Fleur-de-Lis-shi no eizou o goran kudasai.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:34.69,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,Pokémon Trainers...{Pokemon Trainer-tachi yo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.08,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,The future is not yet decided.{Mirai wa mada kimatteinai.}{EN game: the future isn't decided.}{JP game: 未来は　決まっていない=The future isn't decided.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:42.38,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,You have the power \N to change the world.{Kimi-tachi ni wa, sekai o kaeru chikara ga aru.}{EN game: means you have the potential to change the future!}{JP game: 未来を　変える 可能性を　持つ　者！=means you have the possibility to change the future!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.20,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,Please lend me your help...{Akarui mirai o tsukuru tame ni,}{EN game: to help build a brighter future.}{JP game: 輝かしい　未来の　ため=For a shining future}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.57,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,...to build a brighter future.{chikara o kashite kudasai.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.37,Main,Fleur-de-Lis,0,0,0,,I bid you adieu.{Soredewa.}
